note right of HR
  Authorization for these is imperative and organization-scoped:
  `_authService.AuthorizeAsync(userId, orgId, "permission:name:SCOPETYPE:scopeId")`
  inside the controller body — not an attribute. An ORGANIZATION-scoped
  grant implicitly covers child WORKSPACE scopes
  (PermissionEvaluator.cs:95,111).
end note

