note bottom of AIService
  The Core API is always the *caller* into CVerify.AI over the
  named HttpClient "AiServiceClient" (5-min timeout), every request
  HMAC-signed by HmacSignatureService. The one reverse call is the AI
  service fetching `GET api/v1/ai-jobs/{jobId}/artifacts/{key}`.
end note

